---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Digital Nomad Visa Greece | Taxomade">
  <!-- Hero Section with Grid Background -->
  <div class="relative pt-40 pb-32 overflow-hidden bg-slate-50">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/50 via-white/80 to-slate-50"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-tight">Your Digital Nomad Visa for Greece <br/><span class="text-blue-800">—</span> handled for you.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Live legally in Greece while working remotely. We prepare and manage your entire application.</p>
      <a href="/#configurator" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold rounded-lg text-white bg-slate-900 hover:bg-blue-800 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-sm">
        Check if you qualify
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Two-column: What it is & Requirements -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
      <!-- What it is Card -->
      <section class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-800 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          What it is
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          The Greece Digital Nomad Visa lets non-EU citizens live in Greece for up to 12 months while working remotely for employers or clients <strong class="text-slate-900">outside</strong> Greece. It can be extended into a residence permit for up to two years total. It's designed for remote employees, freelancers and business owners whose income comes from abroad — you cannot work for a Greek employer on this visa.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Requirements Card -->
      <section class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-800 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          Requirements
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-slate-700 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>You must be a <strong class="text-slate-900">non-EU / non-EEA / non-Swiss</strong> citizen.</li>
          <li>Minimum <strong class="text-slate-900">€3,500 net per month</strong> income from outside Greece (+20% for a spouse, +15% per child).</li>
          <li>Proof of remote work: employment contract, client contracts, invoices, payslips.</li>
          <li>Valid passport, private health insurance, clean criminal record, proof of accommodation.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20 bg-slate-50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">How it works</h2>
      
      <div class="mb-10 bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-800 p-5 rounded-r-lg">
        <p class="text-blue-900 font-medium"><em>Important 2026 change:</em> As of February 2026, you must apply at a <strong class="text-blue-900">Greek consulate in your home country before travelling</strong> — in-country applications are no longer possible.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6">
            <span class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold shadow-md">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What you do</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Gather your documents (we tell you exactly which), attend your consulate appointment, and travel to Greece once approved.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6">
            <span class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-800 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold shadow-md">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What Taxomade does</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">We review your situation, prepare and check your full document set, handle translations and legalizations, guide you through the consulate submission, and after arrival help you get your tax number (AFM) and residence permit. Processing typically takes around 1–3 months.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-10 text-sm italic text-center">Government fees (visa fee + €1,016 residence permit fee) are paid by you directly to the authorities and are separate from our service fee.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Package -->
    <section class="max-w-md mx-auto mb-20">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Digital Nomad Visa Package</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6">Full end-to-end management of your DNV application.</p>
          <div class="flex items-baseline mb-8">
            <span class="text-5xl font-black text-slate-900">€1.500</span>
            <span class="text-slate-500 ml-2">/ one-off</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Eligibility check & document review</li>
            <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Document translation & legalization support</li>
            <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Consulate appointment prep</li>
            <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> AFM registration upon arrival</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/#configurator" class="block w-full py-4 px-6 bg-slate-900 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors duration-200 text-center">Start application</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-10 text-center">FAQ</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Can freelancers apply?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Yes — as long as you can document ongoing clients and income from outside Greece.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Can I work for a Greek company?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">No. Your income must come from abroad.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Can my family come?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Yes, with higher income proof (+20% spouse, +15% per child). They can live but not work locally.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Does it lead to tax residency?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">If you stay more than 183 days, yes — and then you may qualify for the 50% tax break (see Article 5C).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">How long is it valid?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">12 months initially, extendable to two years.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
